EN: I don't want you to pay attention to other people's gossip.

ZH: 理睬他的请求是正确的事情。
EN: It is the right thing to acknowledge his request.

ZH: 不要因为争吵而不理睬对方的感受。
EN: Don't disregard the other person's feelings because of an argument.

ZH: 我感到被忽视，因为他不理睬我的存在。
EN: I feel neglected because he ignores my presence.

